            "text_UYA6jf": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h1></h1><p>At <strong>CozyBookNook</strong>, we believe a bookshelf should be more than just storage — it should tell a story.</p><p>Our journey began with a simple idea: to bring warmth, creativity, and a touch of magic into everyday spaces. Book nooks are more than decorative pieces — they are miniature worlds, handcrafted escapes that transform ordinary shelves into glowing scenes of imagination.</p><p>Each design in our collection is carefully selected for its detail, charm, and immersive storytelling. From enchanted libraries to celestial retreats, our DIY kits are made for book lovers, dreamers, and creators who find joy in building something beautiful with their own hands.</p><p>We focus on:</p><p>✨ Thoughtfully curated designs<br/><br/>✨ Relaxing, mindful building experiences<br/><br/>✨ High-quality wooden craftsmanship<br/><br/>✨ Cozy LED lighting that brings each scene to life</p><p>Whether you're creating your own magical corner or searching for the perfect gift, we want every CozyBookNook piece to spark inspiration and wonder.</p><p>This isn’t just décor.<br/><br/>It’s a moment of calm.<br/><br/>A creative escape.<br/><br/>A tiny world between your books.</p><p>Welcome to CozyBookNook — where imagination lives on your shelf.</p>",
